Key wiring (ESP32)

RC522 RFID (SPI): SDA=5, SCK=18, MOSI=23, MISO=19, RST=22
MPU6050 (I2C): SDA=21, SCL=22 (move RC522 RST to 4 if you prefer shared 22 for I2C)
I2C LCD: shares I2C SDA=21/SCL=22
LED Strip (WS2812): DIN=27, 5V from USB (with common GND)
Piezo Buzzer: GPIO26 (PWM)
Vibration motor (optional): GPIO25 via N-MOSFET + flyback diode
Camera: feeds the Vision Worker (USB/RTSP). ESP32 only receives AI events over MQTT.

MQTT topics
Publish (ESP32 → Cloud)
minddesk/<deskId>/status → {occupied, rssi, tilt, ts}
minddesk/<deskId>/incident → {type: posture|stranger|overstay, ts}

Subscribe (Cloud → ESP32)
minddesk/<deskId>/command → {led: off/amber/red, buzz: ms}
minddesk/<deskId>/event/posture → {state: ok|slouch|sleep}
minddesk/<deskId>/reserve → {userId, expires}
minddesk/<deskId>/leave_pending → {deadline}
